<br>
Oh and while you might be able to get a group in EC for orcs with the setup you described, I darre you to go solo all of solb with that warrior package.  For 120k you can get a package that lets you tank better and outdamage by 2-1 people who have spent months farming TOV for armor and killing hard mobs for teir weapons.  <br>
<br>
The fact that you can just buy your epic for 20k should be a big clue as to why people are not sympathetic towards the monk community atm.  Do you know that the green scale on the warrior epic alone runs 100-200k IF you can even find one for sale?  How about the SK epic where 173 Ashenbone drake kills later I still havent seen a hide?  Christ, 20k would not even fund the trip to sky for one part of the Warrior/Necro/Mage/SK epics.  While were are talking about weapons, how about that Tstaff that you can get 10 feet inside Karnors, while my vastly inferior one hander drops off of Lord Yelinak and my 2 hander (comparable in ratio but half your DPS due to our anemic hit rate and your outrageous offensive tables) drops off of a TOVN dragon.  But please, I know it must be hard not being able to solo for a fungi so I feel your pain.<br>
<br>
Fact is, those of you who are uber twink jobs who go for the power and changed to monk mid Velious won't notice any change in your soloing or grouping.  Those of you decked out in VT gear and/or those who have played monks since kearly kunark or before will note the change when offtanking on raids, bitch a little, and adjust accordingly.  You still have the best universal DPS around (Rogues are situational), you still have a non interuptable FD with stone stance for the occasional failure, you still have mend, and you still have the supremely highest avoidance of any class.  I think your not in any danger of being kicked off raids.  The day someone tells you that they would rather you play your Beastlord Alt or Necromancer alt and camp your monk nearby in case some monk only loot drops that would otherwise rot, then you will have my sympathy. <p>In your spare time you will study the word of god, and my god says this:  Get a sword, get on a horse, and go kill anyone who is not like you.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bmonklybusiness43508.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=fopoodzo>Fopoodzo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master</span><br>  Posts: 834<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/10/02 1:52:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm17.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=124.topic&index=50>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: We are a Despised Class</span><hr size=1> Hehe hate monks much?  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ugravdigr23.showPublicProfile?language=EN>gravdigr23</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk</span><br>  Posts: 120<br>